"title": "1193: glory, revelation of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1193",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's majestic brilliance shown to the world through Israel and the church, and supremely in and through Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed in nature</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">PSA 19:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3-Ps29:9\">PSA 29:3–29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1-Ps104:4\">PSA 104:1–104:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed through Israel</h2>\n<h3>In the exodus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:11\">EXO 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:7\">EXO 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:10\">EXO 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:9-Exod24:11\">EXO 24:9–24:11</a></p>\n<h3>At his sanctuary</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">EXO 40:34–40:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:43\">EXO 29:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:6\">LEV 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:23\">LEV 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:6\">NUM 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1KI 8:10–8:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13-2Chr5:14\">2CH 5:13–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1-2Chr7:3\">2CH 7:1–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1\">ISA 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:4\">EZK 44:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:7\">HAG 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>In the nation as a whole</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:23\">ISA 44:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:9\">PSA 85:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:6-Isa43:7\">ISA 43:6–43:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:13\">ISA 46:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:3\">ISA 49:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:5\">ISA 55:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:4-Zech2:5\">ZEC 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>To individuals in Israel</h3>\n<p>Moses:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:15-Exod24:17\">EXO 24:15–24:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:18-Exod33:23\">EXO 33:18–33:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:23\">EZK 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:4\">EZK 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:18-Ezek10:19\">EZK 10:18–10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:22-Ezek11:23\">EZK 11:22–11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:2-Ezek43:5\">EZK 43:2–43:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed through the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:12\">EPH 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:21\">EPH 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed to the whole earth</h2>\n<h3>To all peoples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:5\">PSA 57:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:5\">PSA 108:5</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:3\">HAB 3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:11\">PSA 57:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:19\">PSA 72:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:5\">ISA 40:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed in his judgments</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:1-Rev19:2\">REV 19:1–19:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:10\">NUM 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:21-Num14:23\">NUM 14:21–14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:19-Num16:20\">NUM 16:19–16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:10\">ISA 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:19\">ISA 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:21\">ISA 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:21\">EZK 39:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:8\">REV 15:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed in the future</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:19-Isa60:20\">ISA 60:19–60:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:5\">ISA 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:23\">ISA 24:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:2\">ISA 35:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:8\">ISA 58:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:1-Isa60:2\">ISA 60:1–60:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed through Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ reveals God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:9\">LUK 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:40\">JHN 11:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:8-John14:9\">JHN 14:8–14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55\">ACT 7:55</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ reveals his own glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:32\">LUK 9:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:11\">JHN 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:41\">JHN 12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16-2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:16–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Glory revealed in Jesus Christ's death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23\">JHN 12:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27-John12:33\">JHN 12:27–12:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31-John13:32\">JHN 13:31–13:32</a></p>\n<h3>Glory revealed at Jesus Christ's second coming</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">MRK 8:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:26\">LUK 9:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">MAT 24:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">MRK 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">MAT 25:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed in the new Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:10-Rev21:11\">REV 21:10–21:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:23\">REV 21:23</a></p>",
